
Kjots - note taker
------------------

NOTE:
If you upgrade from a version _before_ 0.2.2:
 Edit your .kjotsrc file and remove the last ',' at the
 end of the lines:
 Folders=item1, item2,
                     ^ - remove it !
 Hotlist=item1, item2,
                     ^ - remove it !

You need:
- ktoolpics-0.2
- qt 1.2
- libkde-970510

do:

- set KDEDIR and QTDIR
- make 
- make install

this will install:

$(KDEDIR)/bin/kjots
$(KDEDIR)/doc/HTML/kjots/
$(KDEDIR)/doc/HTML/kjots/kjots.html
$(KDEDIR)/apps/Utilities/
$(KDEDIR)/apps/Utilities/Kjots.kdelnk
$(KDEDIR)/lib/pics/jots.xpm
$(KDEDIR)/lib/pics/filedel.xpm
$(KDEDIR)/lib/pics/OpenBook.xpm

